Privacy Policy
Last Updated: [02/12/2025]

[UNIQQUE] ("we", "our", or "us") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your information when you use our mobile application and services.

1. Information We Collect
1.1 Personal Information
When you use our app, we may collect:

Account Information: Name, email address, phone number, profile picture

Delivery Information: Delivery address, location data

Payment Information: Payment method details (processed securely through third-party processors)

Order History: Previous orders, favorite restaurants, preferences

Contact Information: For customer support and communication

1.2 Automatically Collected Information
Device Information: Device type, operating system, unique device identifiers

Usage Data: App interaction, features used, time spent

Location Data: With your permission, we collect precise or approximate location for delivery services

Log Information: IP address, browser type, access times

1.3 Restaurant/Business Information
If you're a restaurant owner using our platform:

Business Details: Restaurant name, address, contact information

Menu Information: Product details, prices, images

Business Documents: Licenses, certifications (where required)

2. How We Use Your Information
We use the collected information to:

Provide, maintain, and improve our services

Process orders and payments

Facilitate food delivery

Communicate with you about orders, promotions, and updates

Personalize your experience

Ensure security and prevent fraud

Comply with legal obligations

Analyze usage patterns to enhance user experience

3. Information Sharing and Disclosure
We may share your information with:

Restaurants: To fulfill your orders

Delivery Partners: To deliver your orders

Payment Processors: To process transactions securely

Service Providers: For analytics, customer support, and marketing

Legal Authorities: When required by law or to protect rights

We do not sell your personal information to third parties.

4. Data Security
We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information, including:

Encryption of sensitive data

Secure payment processing

Regular security assessments

Access controls and authentication

5. Your Rights and Choices
You have the right to:

Access your personal information

Correct inaccurate information

Delete your account and data

Opt-out of marketing communications

Withdraw location permissions

Export your data

To exercise these rights, contact us at [oramadev.agency@gmail.com].

6. Location Services
We request location permission to:

Show nearby restaurants

Provide accurate delivery estimates

Track delivery progress (if applicable)

Improve location-based recommendations

You can disable location services in your device settings at any time.

7. Children's Privacy
Our services are not directed to children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child under 13, we will take steps to delete such information.

8. Third-Party Services
Our app may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties. We encourage you to read their privacy policies.

9. Data Retention
We retain your personal information only as long as necessary to:

Fulfill the purposes outlined in this policy

Comply with legal obligations

Resolve disputes

Enforce our agreements

10. International Data Transfers
If you are located outside [Your Country], please note that we may transfer your information to servers located in [Your Country] or other countries for processing.

11. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page and updating the "Last Updated" date.

12. Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:

Email: [oramadev.agency@gmail.com]
Address: [maroc]
Website: [oramadev.com]

13. Consent
By using our application, you consent to our Privacy Policy and agree to its terms.

